description.en: TempleDAO is designed on strong principles: building the Temple for the long-term, community first and fairly in all aspects, and prioritising stable wealth creation. Our innovative mechanics including safe minting, intrinsic value backed rewards, safe harvest, price defence incentives, and exit queue.
